text: Jasper County is the ninth studio album by Trisha Yearwood. The album was released on September 13, 2005. It was her first studio album in 4 years. The album was also the return of producer Garth Fundis who produced her Greatest hits album. It was ninth and final studio album of label MCA Nashville Records. == References == Category:2005 albums
title: Jasper County (album)
